attributes.content: The scorching sun, the wilds, the golden sand, and the warm breeze! Woohoo! I feel a new song coming on!
attributes.name: Dan

attributes.content: (Solo)
attributes.name: Frost

attributes.content: Could the both of you quiet down?
attributes.name: Aya

attributes.content: Please. It’s not often we get such a peaceful environment with no one chasing us. Can’t we just have a nice, quiet rest?
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: But Alty, I can smell the sea from here. Are you sure we’re safe?
attributes.name: Aya

attributes.content: Aya, could you not spoil the mood for once?
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: Nowhere in the world is truly safe, but we have to learn to let ourselves relax sometimes.
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: Maybe you’re right.
attributes.name: Aya

attributes.content: So what’s the next step? How are we going to broaden our path? We can’t go back empty-handed.
attributes.name: Aya

attributes.content: At least that doctor gave us an answer this time.
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: Alty looks at the 'key' in her hand.
Really? That looks like something special. And she just gave it to you? What did you trade for it?
attributes.name: Dan

attributes.content: Knowledge.
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: And was that a fair trade?
attributes.name: Dan

attributes.content: I’m not sure. But I think that doctor wants us to put this knowledge to use.
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: Wouldn’t she know?
attributes.name: Aya

attributes.content: We know a lot, she should just...
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: ...If you think about it, the real trade was her using our curiosity to get us to act.
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: So, that means she didn’t pay anything?
attributes.name: Dan

attributes.content: Hm...
attributes.name: Aya

attributes.content: Hm...
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: We’ve been cheated.
attributes.name: Aya

attributes.content: More like baited.
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: Directed?
attributes.name: Dan

attributes.content: Guided.
attributes.name: Frost

attributes.content: Is that doctor really so important?
attributes.name: Aya

attributes.content: No. I think she’s trying to tell us that her actions have no impact at all.
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: What matters is what we think and what we do.
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: Then what about the key? Should we go?
attributes.name: Aya

attributes.content: Ugh, this sucks. Could we not go?
attributes.name: Dan

attributes.content: I’m thinking it’s sort of like music... Our power should not be to force change onto others, we should just be singing our own songs.
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: Sing for them. If it sounds good—
attributes.name: Aya

attributes.content: Then they’ll sing too.
attributes.name: Dan

attributes.content: (Solo)
attributes.name: Frost

attributes.content: Hah, then we will give even more knowledge, and the key, over to the one who is ready.
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: And who will that be?
attributes.name: Aya

attributes.content: I don’t know.
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: Maybe they haven’t been born yet.
attributes.name: Aya

attributes.content: That would be great!
attributes.name: Dan

attributes.content: No it wouldn’t, Dan. We... hm?
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: What is it, Alty?
attributes.name: Aya

attributes.content: The car’s dead.
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: Didn’t you prep it?
attributes.name: Aya

attributes.content: Yes, but we took that detour.
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: And I have to admit, it’s really easy to lose your heading in the middle of the wilderness with no roads or signs.
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: So basically, we’re lost?
attributes.name: Aya

attributes.content: I’m not sure that’s how I’d put it. It’s not so much that we’re off course as it is we’re carving a new path.
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: We’re lost.
attributes.name: Frost

attributes.content: We’re lost! That’s a pretty good theme.
attributes.name: Dan

attributes.content: You know, Dan, I really wish I could learn some of your optimism. So what are we going to do?
attributes.name: Aya

attributes.content: It looks like there’s a rainforest over that way. Let’s check it out.
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: So, who’s getting out to push?
attributes.name: Aya

attributes.content: We could take turns.
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: Alty.
attributes.name: Aya

attributes.content: What?
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: We’ve got a crowd here.
attributes.name: Aya

attributes.content: Yes, we do.
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: But I don’t know what language they’re speaking.
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: So should we just let them follow us?
attributes.name: Aya

attributes.content: Do you have a better idea?
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: We could kill them all?
attributes.name: Aya

attributes.content: You think you can get Frost and Dan to go along with that?
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: (Strumming and singing)
attributes.name: Frost

attributes.content: &*......%$ ....& (W-What is this sound? And why do I like it so much? !)
attributes.name: Archosauria A

attributes.content: &%......% (I’ve never heard anything like it...)
attributes.name: Archosauria B

attributes.content: Hey, how is everybody?!
attributes.name: Dan

attributes.content: Can you tell me what language you’re speaking?!
attributes.name: Dan

attributes.content: Oh, but I guess even if you told me, I still wouldn’t know.
attributes.name: Dan

attributes.content: ......%&$ (Where did they come from?!)
attributes.name: Archosauria C

attributes.content: $......&# (And why does this one look so weird? )
attributes.name: Archosauria D

attributes.content: Well, at least there are people here.
attributes.name: Aya

attributes.content: I just hope there’s a place we can resupply.
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: Wishful thinking.
attributes.name: Aya

attributes.content: You’re outsiders?
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: Huh? You speak Sargonian?
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: Yes, it looks like you’re definitely outsiders.
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: What are you doing here?
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: Our car died, so we’re looking for someone with the Arts to recharge it.
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: ...Come with me.
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: See, Aya, that was more than just wishful thinking.
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: Fine. I guess the world is a magical place.
attributes.name: Aya

attributes.content: Hey hey hey! What’s this?!
attributes.name: Dan

attributes.content: There’s a village here in the middle of this primeval forest!
attributes.name: Dan

attributes.content: (Humming)
attributes.name: Frost

attributes.content: It’s really amazing. You can see the influence of modern architecture on most of the buildings, but they still have that primitive beauty.
attributes.name: Aya

attributes.content: It’s odd, but very special.
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: I am the leader of this tribe, Zumama. Most of my people can understand your language.
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: I can have some of our priests recharge your vehicle, but there are terms.
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: What terms?
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: I want to look inside your vehicle, at its structure.
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: ...Is that all?
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: Yes.
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: Are you sure you won’t break it?
attributes.name: Aya

attributes.content: I’m pretty sure.
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: Alty?
attributes.name: Aya

attributes.content: It’s not like we have a choice.
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: Agreed.
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: Good.  High Priest...
attributes.name: Eunectes

attributes.content: I’m here! ...Oh?
attributes.name: High Priest

attributes.content: Hmmmmm....?
attributes.name: High Priest

attributes.content: I know of you...
attributes.name: High Priest

attributes.content: I know of you...
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: I never expected to see your kind here.
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: Oh, honestly, I was thinking the exact same thing.
attributes.name: High Priest

attributes.content: But I’m more interested in your vehicle than you!
attributes.name: High Priest

attributes.content: By all means.
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: I said it before and I’ll say it again. The world is a magical place.
attributes.name: Aya

attributes.content: I have to say, I agree.
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: At the same time, Frost hooks her guitar up to the ceremonial speaker and improvises a solo.
Nice, Frost.
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: This village is inspiring me.
attributes.name: Frost

attributes.content: Awesome, Frost, you really switched up the melody this time.
attributes.name: Dan

attributes.content: Heat, repressed...
attributes.name: Frost

attributes.content: I’ll call this song... 'D'!
attributes.name: Frost

attributes.content: Where’s that sound coming from?
attributes.name: Archosauria A

attributes.content: What is it?I can feel it energizing me!
attributes.name: Archosauria B

attributes.content: It must be the outsiders who just came! Let’s go see!
attributes.name: Archosauria C

attributes.content: There are more of them, Alty...
attributes.name: Aya

attributes.content: That’s not good.
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: These lives thirst for music! For energy! For...
attributes.name: Frost

attributes.content: What a voice!
attributes.name: Archosauria B

attributes.content: Outsider, give us more music!
attributes.name: Archosauria C

attributes.content: Alty... I know it’s unexpected, but I think the atmosphere here is actually really good.
attributes.name: Aya

attributes.content: Why don’t we get out the amps and play together?
attributes.name: Aya

attributes.content: I guess that would be fine.
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: Yeah, can’t let Frost take all the glory!
attributes.name: Dan

attributes.content: I gotta get in on such a badass track!
attributes.name: Dan

attributes.content: Then let the locals feel the music of AUS!
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: It’s just a few notes, but I’m too excited to sit still!
attributes.name: Archosauria A

attributes.content: It might be like what the priests do, it’s called 'music'?
attributes.name: Archosauria B

attributes.content: I’ve never heard anything like it! Who are these people?!
attributes.name: Archosauria C

attributes.content: I know, they must be 'Cuicayotl'!
attributes.name: Archosauria D

attributes.content: 'Cuicayotl'?  What’s that?
attributes.name: Dan

attributes.content: Oh, that’s how you say 'one who sings' in their language.
attributes.name: High Priest

attributes.content: But it’s been a long time since they had a 'Cuicayotl' here, and you’ve won them over with your music.
attributes.name: High Priest

attributes.content: And I must say, your music is vastly different from that of any other 'Cuicayotl' I’ve ever heard before!
attributes.name: High Priest

attributes.content: But no matter. I find yours a lot more fun!
attributes.name: High Priest

attributes.content: 'Cuicayotl', give us another song!
attributes.name: Archosauria E

attributes.content: I’ll give you anything! Just one more song!
attributes.name: Archosauria F

attributes.content: What do we do, Alty?
attributes.name: Aya

attributes.content: Let’s stay here, Alty!
attributes.name: Dan

attributes.content: Well, I can’t let you forget our goal...
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: But, fine. We’ve got time.
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: I never imagined there would be a Messenger here.
attributes.name: Aya

attributes.content: And I never thought AUS, from all the magazine covers, would show up here either.
attributes.name: Inam

attributes.content: Where’s Zumama?
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: She’s making the speaker system you asked for. So I’ll be taking you.
attributes.name: Inam

attributes.content: How long are you going to stay?
attributes.name: Inam

attributes.content: Maybe a week, maybe a month, maybe a whole year.
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: This place is doing it for us. I think we can have some fun here, at least.
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: Then this is the right place for you to put on a show.
attributes.name: Inam

attributes.content: So cool!
attributes.name: Dan

attributes.content: It’s... some kind of temple?
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: That’s right. This is where all the tribes used to gather for the 'Mahuizzotia', but it hasn’t been used since Gavial left.
attributes.name: Inam

attributes.content: 'Mahuizzotia'?
attributes.name: Aya

attributes.content: Gavial? That name came up at Rhodes Island... No, it’s probably just a common name.
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: You can perform here.
attributes.name: Inam

attributes.content: We’re going to give the people the best music they’ve ever heard.
attributes.name: Frost

attributes.content: Yes, hahaha! Yes! We’ll leave the mark of AUS right here!
attributes.name: Dan

attributes.content: Two months later...
AUS is unbelievable...
attributes.name: Inam

attributes.content: They actually did stay for two whole months.
attributes.name: Inam

attributes.content: If Gavial ever comes back, she’s going to be blown away by the music we have way out here now.
attributes.name: Inam

attributes.content: The people fell in love with their rock and roll.
attributes.name: Inam

attributes.content: So what are they going to perform for us today?
attributes.name: Inam

attributes.content: ...I wonder maybe if I’m their biggest fan.
attributes.name: Inam

attributes.content: AUS...
attributes.name: Inam

attributes.content: Huh?
attributes.name: Inam

attributes.content: The room is empty. All the toiletries and bedding are neat and tidy, with a piece of paper resting on the table in the center.
They’re gone?
attributes.name: Inam

attributes.content: There’s a note on the table. Let’s see...
attributes.name: Inam

attributes.content: 'We left. Don’t miss us. I hope you enjoyed the music. Also, we left all our records here for you. Have fun.  -AUS'
attributes.name: Inam

attributes.content: ...Heh, they really are unbelievable.
attributes.name: Inam

attributes.content: I don’t think I’ll ever forget that Acahualla place.
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: (Humming) It was definitely unforgettable.
attributes.name: Frost

attributes.content: But the people there are really noisy, and wild.
attributes.name: Aya

attributes.content: Yeah? I love them!
attributes.name: Dan

attributes.content: Of course you do. I don’t think you’d mind if we left you there.
attributes.name: Aya

attributes.content: I was definitely thinking about it.
attributes.name: Dan

attributes.content: Don’t you think those people have a kind of natural, primal energy?
attributes.name: Dan

attributes.content: Out of all the countries and cities we’ve been to, I’ve never seen people like that.
attributes.name: Dan

attributes.content: I love ‘em!
attributes.name: Dan

attributes.content: Well, you’re right about that much.
attributes.name: Aya

attributes.content: They really get our music. They’re the best audience we’ve ever had.
attributes.name: Frost

attributes.content: I think Frost likes them too.
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: But we can’t just show up and flip a whole civilization upside-down. We should stick to singing.
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: Sing for them. If it sounds good—
attributes.name: Aya

attributes.content: Then they’ll sing too.
attributes.name: Dan

attributes.content: Didn’t we say that before?
attributes.name: Aya

attributes.content: Who knows? We might’ve said it a million times already.
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: Let’s go. Continue on our journey.
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: If we sing to the world, will she listen?
attributes.name: Alty

attributes.content: A few of the bandmates joke around for a bit, until the car goes silent.
Alty looks at the key in her hand, 'Dr. Kal'tsit, can that Rhodes Island of yours give the world the answer it’s looking for?'
